r3011 | andlov | 2017-09-18 17:39:50 +0200 (Mon, 18 Sep 2017) | 1 line

The mediator is a frontend for various handlers: complex, direct, readonce, request and simple defining caching strategy. The backend is split in: indexed and native. The old behaviour is preserved using complex as handler with indexed cache as backend.
