r2911 | andlov | 2017-03-28 21:50:51 +0200 (Tue, 28 Mar 2017) | 1 line

Adding exclude filter for query result (false, null, empty and count on result set). Moved housekeep to coherence class. Don't use the entry class for serialized data in normal case (only needed for coherence check). Minimize CPU, memory and cache space use by disable cache coherence check. Empty result sets are not cached by default (using exclude -> result -> empty == true).
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2910 | andlov | 2017-03-28 16:07:57 +0200 (Tue, 28 Mar 2017) | 1 line

