r2425 | andlov | 2016-06-08 00:43:10 +0200 (Wed, 08 Jun 2016) | 1 line

Each cache save() leaks/consumes ~1 MB of RAM. Grow memory_limit to prevent 'availible memory exhausted' fatal error. Out of memory/swap is a better option that HTTP 500 in some cases. Best is to never call cache save() in a large loop, but in reality thats hard to prevent.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2424 | andlov | 2016-06-07 12:55:47 +0200 (Tue, 07 Jun 2016) | 1 line

Prevent cache save() from exhausting available process memory.
