r2109 | andlov | 2015-03-13 04:32:38 +0100 (Fri, 13 Mar 2015) | 1 line

Unified error and exception handling in all controllers. Triggered errors and thrown exceptions in dispatcher, controller initialize and actions are reported back to client in a sub system dependent format (e.g. thru error page or by SOAP fault).
