------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2105 | andlov | 2015-03-11 16:46:34 +0100 (Wed, 11 Mar 2015) | 1 line

Bug fix: Returning false for exceptions trapped by beforeException() will prevent action to be forwarded to target controller (e.g. AJAX) leaving an empty response on client side. This fix will duplicate error logging for exceptions unless we filter on exception type (e.g. dispatch exceptions).
------------------------------------------------------------------------
