r297 | andlov | 2010-08-24 11:53:57 +0200 (Tue, 24 Aug 2010) | 1 line

Added test case mode for examinations. This mode allows users to preview and taking exams on a copy of the original exam. The exam can then be corrected, decoded or deleted. In essential, this can be thought of as a non-destructive and safe demo and dry-run mode ;-)
